title: When Do You Stop Eating Thanksgiving leftovers?
itunes:title: When Do You Stop Eating Thanksgiving leftovers?
description:
Monday 11/27 - Today on the show, we opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought about the Cam'ron and Mase diss tracks they made for each other over the weekend, and even though many listeners thought Mase won the battle, many other listeners thought that both rapper should just have a seat. Also, Thanksgiving just past and many are still eating left overs, but what is the cut off date? we opened up the phone lines to see when they stop eating leftovers. Moreover, Charlamagne gave him "Donkey of the Day" to Post Malone after he made comments about not going to "Hip Hop" music if you want to think about life, lyrics and ect.
